data.description: Better than brand new home in sought after St. Michael's Bay in the East Forsyth District! This 3 year old home truly is ready to go for all of your needs. The sellers have taken immaculate care of everything. The backyard oasis is absolutely gorgeous with a RESORT STYLE pool only 2 years old, covered pavilion to entertain, watch games, movie nights, etc. with plenty of seating, outdoor heaters, wiring for speakers, fully fenced in backyard and covered patio area off of the kitchen. Plus the level backyard is perfect for outdoor games, pets and kids. Inside the home you'll find the most functional floor plan in the neighborhood that has master on main, office space, living/dining room, large open kitchen with island, laundry on main, half bath, and ample space for a kitchen table that could seat 6-8 people. The kitchen has double ovens, gas cook top, the most counter space than any other floor plan, and seating at the island. Engineered hardwood floors are throughout the main level. Upstairs includes 3 large bedrooms that would all fit a king bed and walk in closets. One bedroom contains it's own full bathroom while the other 2 bedrooms are connected with a jack and jill bathroom! To finish out the upstairs level you'll find a bonus room for a second media space/ kids space, craft room/ second office, etc. The added 3rd car tandem garage is positioned perfectly with a door to the pool area to make storage of items easy and accessible. The possibilities are endless! St. Michael's Bay amenities are top notch with pickle ball, tennis, clubhouse, pool, green space, and a community marina. Pull your boat up to one of the 4 spots for the day, fish, kayak, paddle board, swim, etc from the dock!
